; Coverage for report.cc lines 968-982: fn_nail_down with amount type
; When --historical is used, amounts are nailed down to market value

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --historical Assets:Stocks
24-Jan-01 Buy                   Assets:Stocks              $1500.00     $1500.00
end test
